### FAQ
#### What do I do if I encounter an error?
If you encounter an error while using Workplace 2, please contact your Workplace 2 administrator. It may be helpful to provide the following information:

- Description of the problem

- Error code and message

- Business Case name

- Technical IDs of the task and process

- Version number of Workplace 2 and Composer

- Screenshots

#### Where can I find the version number of Workplace 2?
To find the version number of your Workplace 2 application, click **Account** in the lower left corner of the screen. The version, build-hash and build-date of your Workplace 2 application can be found beneath the language switcher. This information may be helpful when troubleshooting application errors. Click **Copy info to clipboard** to share it with your Workplace 2 administrator.
